n \geq 1
\sum^n_{i=1}\left(1 + \dfrac{1}{n}\right)
n
S=\left(1 + \dfrac{1}{n}\right) \times n=(n+1)
S=\sum^n_{i=1}\left(1 + \dfrac{1}{n}\right)
S=\sum^n_{i=1}\left(1 + \dfrac{1}{n}\right)=\left(1 + \dfrac{1}{n}\right)+\left(1 + \dfrac{1}{n}\right)+\left(1 + \dfrac{1}{n}\right)+...+\left(1 + \dfrac{1}{n}\right)
S=\sum^n_{i=1}\left(1 + \dfrac{1}{i}\right)
S=\sum^n_{i=1} 1 +\sum^n_{i=1}\dfrac{1}{i}=n+H_n
